0 TOGGLE~
Syntax: {ctoggle{x <option>
 
Toggles given option on/off. Available options are:
{caffects{x    - defines whether spells affecting you will be shown in score
             or not. See {CHELP AFFECTS{x.
{cbrief{x      - with this option turned on you will not see room descriptions
             when walking. Just room names.
{ccolor{x      - turns ANSI color codes ON/OFF. See {CHELP COLOR{x
{ccompact{x    - turn this option ON to skip empty line before your prompt.
{ccombine{x    - defines whether same items in your inventory will be combined
             (shown with numbers) or shown separated.
{clong flags{x - toggles oldstyle flag view, like ({MPink Aura{x)({RRed Aura{x)...
             New format looks like [[{y.{D.{m.{c.{MP{D.{G.{b.{RR{Y.{W.{y.{g.{g.{x]. See {CHELP FLAGS{x.
{cnobust{x     - will not send you new prompt each time your hp/mana/moves have
             changed. Useful to avoid spam from regeneration.
{cnoflee{x     - with this option turned on, your character will not attempt
             to flee when disconnected. See {CHELP FLEE{x.
{cnotelnet{x   - disables telnet parser. See {CHELP RUSSIAN{x for details.
{cnoiac{x      - capitalizes small russian 'ya'. See {CHELP RUSSIAN{x
{cnoverbose{x  - disables verbose messages (e.g. [excellent] for items etc.)
{cprompt{x     - enables/disable prompt showing.
{ctelnet GA{x  - some clients require special symbol (GA) to be sent to them.
{cquiet edit{x - buffer all output when you write a note.
~
